## Dependencies

### Runtime (Isaac Sim loads these via `extension.toml`)

- `omni.kit.uiapp`
- `omni.ui`
- `omni.usd`
- `omni.kit.viewport.utility`
- `omni.replicator.core`
- `isaacsim.core.api`
- `isaacsim.core.utils`

### Python (for CLI + tests)

- `pyyaml` (CLI)
- `pytest` (tests)

